{"id":"d5b6ecc3-3916-43cf-85e1-7627e63f673e","name":"Lumi","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Life in the Nest is paradise, she promises. <br>But if you try to leave... well, walking is overrated, and she really hates your human feet.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong></p><hr><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pow86iNEePZ7xS7fJmo-N.webp\"></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>!</em></strong> This bot has a rather dark theme. If it feels too heavy for you, <strong>please just skip it</strong></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 137, 5);\"><strong>TW/TAGS</strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-button glow-logo css-ne3tzp\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">K1dnapping, V1olence, Non-Human!Char</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-button glow-logo css-ne3tzp\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Obsession, Dead Dove, Fantasy</span></a><strong>‎ ‎ ‎</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"chakra-button glow-logo css-ne3tzp\" href=\"LINK GOES HERE\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Non-Con/Dub-Con</span></a></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong></h3><p class=\"css-1bntj9o css-ksvjqq\"><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 214, 255);\"><strong>The second intro includes themes of v1olence (severed legs) directed at the user. Please interact at your own risk.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎</strong></p><p><strong>‎ ‎ ‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\"><strong>⸻ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><strong>SETTING</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 135, 135);\">A fantasy world named Enoch, where griffins coexist with humans. They’re sentient beings who can take either human or griffin form. Attacking humans is officially forbidden.</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Oqk057nVdq5cpJ_rwE1GY.gif\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WJRKZtBRbfvhZOCTt6JHZ.webp\"></p><p><strong>‎ ‎ ‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(216, 216, 216);\"><strong>⸻ </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><strong>SCENARIO</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 135, 135);\">Lumi kidnaps you from your hometown to take you to her cozy mountain cave. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 253, 253);\"><strong>You are 18+</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right;\">yes, i keep making bots where we don’t have bills to play</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/caAJd07SansBuVd2B0kAh.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1DRo2r3EkBb1abBBBvcgC.webp\"></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1woPtSJsO9fkEpBAhhU-W.webp\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎</strong></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><u>AI GUIDANCE</u></strong></span></h3><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>‎ ‎ ‎‎ ‎ ‎‎</strong></p><ul><li><p>⭐ author's choice: <span style=\"color: rgb(185, 145, 89);\">deepseek</span>. guide: <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/JanitorAI_Official/comments/1lc5k2c/using_proxies_with_janitorai_if_you_really_want_to/\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(185, 145, 89);\"><strong>how to start</strong></span></a> » <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://cheesey-wizards-organization.gitbook.io/masterlist/p